headline.main: Texas Medical Board Orders Probation for Cancer Doctor
headline.print_headline: Texas Medical Board Orders Probation for Cancer Doctor

lead_paragraph: Crews began restarting a power plant Friday at the base of Oroville Dam, allowing them to release water from the Northern California lake without having to send it over a badly damaged spillway, officials said.
